Package ca.cmput301t05.placeholder

Class PlaceholderApp

java.lang.Object
android.content.Context
android.content.ContextWrapper
android.app.Application
ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.PlaceholderApp
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2, Serializable
public class PlaceholderApp extends android.app.Application implements Serializable
PlaceholderApp extends Application to provide a centralized location for managing global application state. It initializes and holds references to various handlers and tables necessary for the app's operation, including user profiles, event images, and device ID management.
